abstract: More Android devices are coming and many of them will not censor their apps.
snippet: More Android devices are coming and many of them will not censor their apps.
lead_paragraph: Summer Of ’09 Phone War update: By year’s end, there will be at least 18 phones on the market worldwide based on the Android operating system, Google disclosed for the first time Wednesday.

headline.main: Google: Expect 18 Android Phones by Year’s End
